messages.messageBody:
> Anyone from the St.Paul, MN area?

Well acording to my 16 YO niece who lives in S. Minneapolis, the Mall of
America is THE place to be. Indoor amusement park, water park, theaters,
and dozens of other attractions. It's the biggest mall in America, and the
second largest in the world (after Edmonton Mall in Canada.)

Nanci K.
